name: As a customer of Bugaboo, Hernandez has a question that needs answering

testSteps.description: 1: As a customer of Bugaboo, Hernandez has a question that needs answering ({question=Delivery, Return or Refund})

children.description: Given Hernandez is a customer of Bugaboo
Hernandez opens the Bugaboo home page
Hernandez opens the Bugaboo home page
Hernandez clicks on BugabooHomePage.acceptAllCookies
Hernandez should see a value that is true
When Hernandez wants to submit a customer contact form
Hernandez opens the Bugaboo Consumer Contact Form page
Hernandez opens the Bugaboo customer contact form
And Hernandez chooses the "Delivery, Return or Refund" question
Hernandez clicks on BugabooCustomerContactForm.openQuestions
And Hernandez chooses one of the available options
Hernandez clicks on <button type='button'> - BugabooCustomerContactForm.answersList
Then Hernandez should see the explanation

Hernandez should see By.xpath: //div[@interop-accordionsection_accordionsection]//*[contains(text(), 'What is your expected shipping timeline?')]/../../../../div[@aria-hidden='false'] that is displayed
